<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165040757544">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165040757546">
<p id="fs-id1165040757549">Find all critical points for <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
