</span>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042066031">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042066034">
<span data-type="media" id="fs-id1165042066039" data-alt="The function graphed starts at (&#8722;2.2, 10), decreases rapidly to (&#8722;2, &#8722;11), increases to (&#8722;1, 5) before decreasing slowly to (1, 3), at which point it increases to (2, 7), and then decreases to (3, &#8722;20).">
