<p id="fs-id1165042066053">Absolute minimum at 3; Absolute maximum at &#8722;2.2; local minima at &#8722;2, 1; local maxima at &#8722;1, 2</p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042066060">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042066062">
<span data-type="media" id="fs-id1165042066068" data-alt="The function graphed starts at (&#8722;3, &#8722;1), increases rapidly to (&#8722;2, 0.7), decreases to (&#8722;1, &#8722;0.25) before decreasing slowly to (1, 0.25), at which point it decreases to (2, 0.7), and then increases to (3, 1).">
