</span>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042066089">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042066091">
<span data-type="media" id="fs-id1165042066097" data-alt="The function graphed starts at (&#8722;2.5, 1), decreases rapidly to (&#8722;2, &#8722;1.25), increases to (&#8722;1, 0.25) before decreasing slowly to (0, 0.2), at which point it increases slowly to (1, 0.25), then decreases rapidly to (2, &#8722;1.25), and finally increases to (2.5, 1).">
